reviewText: I bought this set strictly because I wanted the Christmas with Holly movie, which I couldn't find individually. I haven't watched the other two movies yet
This dvd is in very good condition!!!
One of the dvds skipped a lot but I didn't want to return it for a refund for I thought I might not be able to get a replacement.
Love the movie "Fallen Angel".  The others are good too.
great movies- chick flicks that even men like
I loved the movie Fallen Angel and the other 2 movies were very good too.

It is a beautiful Christmas movie.  Lovely background of a small town and ocean.  Very good acting and a lovely story of patience, sacrifice and taking responsibility for the ones we love.  Also, has a cute dog.
You can buy this on halmark.com for 29.99
